{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-10","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-final-exams-table","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 10","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tvoja tabela je skoro kompletna, ali fali još nešto što moraš da dodaš.</p>\n<p>Bi bi bilo lepo da element <code>td</code> koji se koristi za <code>Average Grade</code> pokriva dve kolone umesto samo jedne.</p>\n<p>Da biste to uradili, možete koristiti atribut <code>&#x3C;dfn>colspan&#x3C;/dfn></code> na elementu <code>td</code>.</p>\n<p>Atribut <code>colspan</code> određuje broj kolona koje ćelija treba da pokrije.</p>\n<p>Evo primera korišćenja atributa <code>colspan</code> za sportsku tabelu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;tr>\n  &#x3C;td colspan=\"3\">Total Points&#x3C;/td>\n&#x3C;/tr>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar otvarajućeg taga <code>td``, dodajte atribut ``colspan`` i podesite ga na ``\"2\"</code>.</p>\n<p>I sa tom promenom, vaša tabela je kompletna!</p>\n</section>","id":"66a9cd4ffa48cf1ef7333640","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-10"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <title>Calculus Final Exams Table</title>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <table>\n      <caption>\n        Calculus Final Exam Grades\n      </caption>\n\n      <thead>     \n        <tr>\n          <th>Last Name</th>\n          <th>First Name</th>\n          <th>Grade</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n   